			"page": 0,
			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Nethermancy",
			"subclassSource": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"level": 2,
			"entries": [
				"Nethermancy是在几百年前巫师们逃到Shadowfell并通过这个平面的许多秘密进行搜索时创造的。最初的尼瑟曼人发现影子魔法是影子城创造的原因。影子魔法的力量来自于原始人第一次赋予物质形式时拒绝的黑暗能量。阴阳师专注于从他们的环境中提取原始的影子，然后将其强行转化为奥术力量，创造出神奇的效果。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Nethermancy Savant|Wizard||Nethermancy|HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy|2"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Being of the Shadow|Wizard||Nethermancy|HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy|2"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Nethermancy Savant",
			"entries": [
				"从2级开始，你必须花费一半的金币和时间来将尼瑟曼的咒语复制到你的法术书中。"
			],
			"source": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"page": 0,
			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Nethermancy",
