			"level": 2,
			"header": 1
		},
		{
			"name": "Being of the Shadow",
			"entries": [
				"从2级开始，在夜间，你在所有依靠力量、灵巧或智力的攻击卷和蓄力动作上都有优势。"
			],
			"source": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"page": 0,
			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Nethermancy",
			"subclassSource": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"level": 2,
			"header": 2
		},
		{
			"name": "Shadowsight",
			"source": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"page": 0,
			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Nethermancy",
			"subclassSource": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"level": 6,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"从6级开始，如果你的法术书中没有黑暗法术，你就把它加到你的法术书中。你可以在神奇的黑暗中看东西，就像它是昏暗的光一样。"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Protection From the Shadows",
			"source": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"page": 0,
			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Nethermancy",
			"subclassSource": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"level": 10,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"从10级开始，你的影子可以变成一个实体，并作为对危险的一种即时的、几乎是本能的反应来保护你。当一个生物对你进行攻击时，你可以用你的反应在攻击者和你之间插入你的影子。攻击会自动错过你，然后影子会恢复到正常状态。一旦你使用这个功能，你就不能再使用它，直到你完成一个短期或长期休息。"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Being of Darkness",
			"source": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"page": 0,
			"className": "Wizard",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Nethermancy",
			"subclassSource": "HFDRWizardSchoolofNethermancy",
			"level": 14,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"从14级开始，你已经学会了与影子融为一体。当你在一个昏暗的光线或黑暗的区域时，你可以使用你的行动来隐身。你会一直保持隐身状态，直到你进行攻击、施法，或处于亮光区域。"
			]
		}
	],
